data.description: Incredible opportunity awaits in this 4 bed, 2.5 bath home nestled in the Bridges community. The open-concept main living area includes a cozy gas fireplace, dining space that leads to the covered deck, & kitchen w/walk-in pantry, granite counters, & generously sized island w/bar seating. You'll also find an office on the main level for added convenience! The large primary bedroom comes complete w/a luxurious 5-piece ensuite bath & walk-in closet. 3 addl bedrooms & a second full bath are located upstairs. Enjoy a spacious loft area that provides addl living space. A/C for those warm summer days. Community also offers access to a nearby park, & the convenience of being located near Hwy 18 & 516, providing easy access to shopping & dining.
